Global Catalytic Converter Market Insights
Catalytic Converter Market size was valued at USD 12.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 18.57 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Catalytic Converter Market Overview
The global catalytic converter market was valued at USD 28.4 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for vehicles equipped with efficient emission control systems, government regulations promoting environmental sustainability, and advancements in catalytic converter technology. With an increase in vehicle production and stringent emission norms globally, the market is witnessing substantial demand across automotive, industrial, and other sectors. The market’s growth is further fueled by rising awareness regarding environmental concerns and the necessity to reduce harmful emissions.

